def generate_y(x, f):
    y = np.sin(2*np.pi * f * x)
    return y

拍音¶

复合频率¶

$$ \begin{align} &\frac{1}{f1} \cdot x = \frac{1}{f2} \cdot y & x, y \in \mathbb{N}_+ \\ &min(x) = \frac{LCM}{f2} \\ &\text{$LCM$ is the least common multiple of $f1$ and $f2$} \\ &T = \frac{1}{f1} \cdot x = \frac{LCM}{f1 \cdot f2} \\ &f = \frac{1}{T} = \frac{f1 \cdot f2}{LCM} \\ &f = \alpha \cdot \frac{f1}{LCM} \cdot f1 & f2 = \alpha \cdot f1 \\ \end{align} $$
In [12]:
# # 
import math

def get_lcm(f1, f2):
    gca = math.gcd(int(f1), int(f2))
    print("gca:", gca)
    # 
    lcm = f1*f2/gca
    print("lcm:", lcm)
    return lcm
In [13]:
def get_f(f1, f2):
    lcm = get_lcm(f1, f2)
    f = f1*f2/lcm
    T = 1/f
    print("f:", f)
    print("T:", T)
    print("f/f1:", f/f1)
    print("f1/f:", f1/f)
    return f

def plot_2_contrast(f_list):
    n = len(f_list)
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6*n))
    for i in range(n):
        f1 = f_list[i][0]
        f2 = f_list[i][1]
        print("==================== 2 ======================")
        print("f1, f2:", f1, f2)
        print("---------------------------------------------")        
        f_2 = get_f(f1, f2)
        t = 2 * (1/f_2)    
        x = np.arange(0, t, 0.001)
        y_f1 = generate_y(x, f1)
        y_f2 = generate_y(x, f2)
        y_2 = np.array([y_f1, y_f2]).sum(axis=0)
        plt.subplot(n, 1, i+1)
        plt.plot(x, y_f1)
        plt.plot(x, y_f2)
        plt.plot(x, y_2, label="f1, f2:" + str(f1) +", "+ str(f2))
        plt.grid()
        plt.legend()

def plot_3_contrast(f_list):
    n = len(f_list)
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6*n))
    for i in range(n):
        f1 = f_list[i][0]
        f2 = f_list[i][1]
        f3 = f_list[i][2]
        print("==================== 3 ======================")
        print("f1, f2, f3:", f1, f2, f3)
        print("-------------------- 2 ----------------------")
        print("f1, f2:", f1, f2)
        f_2 = get_f(f1, f2)
        print("-------------------- 3 ----------------------")
        print("f_2, f3:", f_2, f3)
        f_3 = get_f(f_2, f3)
        
        t = 2 * (1/f_3)    
        x = np.arange(0, t, 0.001)
        y_f1 = generate_y(x, f1)
        y_f2 = generate_y(x, f2)
        y_f3 = generate_y(x, f3)
        y_2 = np.array([y_f1, y_f2]).sum(axis=0)
        y_3 = np.array([y_f1, y_f2, y_f3]).sum(axis=0)
        plt.subplot(n, 1, i+1)
        # plt.plot(x, y_f1)
        # plt.plot(x, y_f2)
        # plt.plot(x, y_f3)
        # plt.plot(x, y_2, label="f1, f2:" + str(f1) +", "+ str(f2))
        plt.plot(x, y_3, label="f1, f2, f3:" + str(f1) +", "+ str(f2) + ", "+ str(f3))
        plt.grid()
        plt.legend(loc="upper right")

def plot_(f1, f2):
    print("==========================================")   
    f2_r = np.round(f2)
    print("f1, f2:", f1, f2)
    print("T:", 1/f1, 1/f2)
    print("f1, f2_r:", f1, f2_r)
    print("T:", 1/f1, 1/f2_r)
    f_2 = get_f(f1, f2_r)
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15, 8))

    t = 2 * (1/f_2)    
    x = np.arange(0, t, 0.001)
    y_f1 = generate_y(x, f1)
    y_f2 = generate_y(x, f2)
    y_f2_r = generate_y(x, f2_r)
    y_2 = np.array([y_f1, y_f2]).sum(axis=0)
    y_2_r = np.array([y_f1, y_f2_r]).sum(axis=0)
    # plt.plot(x, y_f1)
    # plt.plot(x, y_f2)
    plt.plot(x, y_2, label="f1, f2:" + str(f1) +", "+ str(f2))
    plt.plot(x, y_2_r, label="f1, f2:" + str(f1) +", "+ str(f2_r))
